==Awards and honors==
The individuals in the sections below earned recognition for meritorious performances.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://bentley.umich.edu/athdept/football/fbteam/1997fbt.htm|title=1997 Football Team|accessdate=2010-07-08|date=2007-04-09|publisher=The Regents of the University of Michigan }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bigten.org/auto_pdf/p_hotos/s_chools/big10/sports/m-footbl/auto_pdf/FullFBMG|title=Big Ten Conference Football Full Media Guide|accessdate=2010-07-08|date=2010-01-05|publisher=[[CBS Interactive]]/[[Big Ten Conference]]|pages=70&ndash;82}}</ref>

===National===
*All-Americans: [[Charles Woodson]], [[Glen Steele]], [[Jerame Tuman]]
*[[List of Heisman Trophy winners|Heisman Trophy]]: Woodson
*[[Walter Camp Award]]: Woodson
*[[Sporting News College Football Player of the Year]]: Woodson
*[[Chic Harley Award]]: Woodson
*[[Bronko Nagurski Trophy]]: Woodson
*[[Chuck Bednarik Award]]: Woodson
*[[Jim Thorpe Award]]: Woodson
*[[Touchdown Club of Columbus#The_Jack_Tatum_Trophy|Jack Tatum Trophy]]: Woodson
*[[Walter Camp Coach of the Year Award]]: [[Lloyd Carr]]
*[[George Munger Award]]: Carr
*[[Paul "Bear" Bryant Award]]: Carr

===Conference===
{{main|Big Ten Conference football individual honors}}
